channel.title: Mp5 My first SMG model. *First post*
channel.description:
I made a model of a mp5 in 3DS Max. My textures are not working on it at the min for some reason :confused:, but the gun does still look quite good without any textures.
Here it is side on. [IMG]http://i428.photobucket.com/albums/qq3/dave_02_2008/Mp5sideon.jpg[/img]
Here are the iron sights. [IMG]http://i428.photobucket.com/albums/qq3/dave_02_2008/Mp5ironsightes.jpg[/img]
Here it is from a angle. [IMG]http://i428.photobucket.com/albums/qq3/dave_02_2008/Mp5bottom.jpg[/img]
I will update when i get the textures working.
